These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, cola, milk, mirinda
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, ferret, rat
1. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking tea is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
5. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | tea | cola | mirinda | milk |
| Pet        | chinchilla | hamster   | rat | ferret    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, drama, mystery, adventure
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, thai, colombian, egyptian
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the italian is on the left of the colombian##1
3. the colombian is in an odd position##4
4. the italian is the person watching animation movies##1
5. the thai is on the right of the colombian##1
6. the italian is the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | animation  | drama  | adventure |
| Nationality   | egyptian    | italian | colombian | thai    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, cauliflower, cucumber, radish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, scientific, musical, fantasy
1. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
2. the person eating cucumber is in an even position##4
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating cucumber##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | radish | cucumber | cauliflower    | pear      |
| Movie-Genre   | musical        | fantasy     | mystery | scientific |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks, video-games, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, d&b, techno, metal
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the fan of jazz and the fan of metal##2
2. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the fan of techno is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | puzzles | fishing | magic-tricks | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | techno       | jazz   | d&b    | metal  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, gospel, r&b, classical
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, italian, dutch, canadian
1. the fan of r&b is on the right of the canadian##1
2. the italian is the fan of classical##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
4. the fan of gospel is on the far left##1
5. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4
6. the malaysian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | salsa    | r&b   | classical       |
| Nationality   | malaysian | canadian | dutch | italian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, scientific, action, martial-arts
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, dutch, brazilian, mexican
1. the dutch is in an even position##4
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the dutch##1
3. the person watching action movies is in an odd position##4
4. the indian is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the brazilian is on the left or right of the indian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | scientific | martial-arts | superhero |
| Nationality   | mexican | dutch     | indian  | brazilian  |

