.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, superhero, spy, zombie
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, skateboard, helicopter, motorbike
1. the person driving the motorbike is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person driving the boat##3
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | zombie | spy | superhero    |
| Transport     | motorbike | helicopter  | boat     | skateboard |

