.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, dancer, nurse, security-guard
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, frog, turtle, chinchilla
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the dancer##3
2. the security-guard is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the security-guard##3
4. the security-guard is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the designer is between the security-guard and the dancer##2
6. the owner of the frog is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the frog is between the designer and the owner of the turtle##2
8. the designer is on the left or right of the dancer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | dancer | designer      | security-guard | nurse |
| Pet   | goldfish  | chinchilla | frog    | turtle            |

