.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
There 4 different types of food: radish, carrot, eggplant, corn
4 different pets are kept: ferret, goldfish, pony, goat
1. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
2. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
3. the owner of the ferret is between the owner of the goldfish and the person eating eggplant##2
4. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating eggplant is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | corn | carrot   | radish | eggplant |
| Pet    | goat     | goldfish | ferret     | pony  |

