.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, tea, water, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, metal, rock, r&b
1. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of r&b##1
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the fan of r&b is between the fan of folk and the person drinking water##2
4. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
6. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | tea       | water   | lemonade | iced-tea |
| Music-Genre   | rock | metal | r&b        | folk    |

