.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, soy-milk, cola
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, skiing, lacrosse, handball
1. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | cola   | almond-milk      | soy-milk      |
| Sport      | skiing | lacrosse | handball | surfing |

