.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, plum, raspberry, corn
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, salsa, dubstep, electronic
1. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of country##1
2. the fan of dubstep is in an even position##4
3. the person eating plum is in an even position##4
4. the person eating peach is on the far right##1
5. the person eating raspberry is between the fan of salsa and the fan of dubstep##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | corn | plum  | raspberry  | peach |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | dubstep | country | salsa   |

