.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, singing, filmmaking, camping
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, basketball, biathlon, volleyball
1. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who's hobby is singing##2
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | camping | singing         | reading   | filmmaking |
| Sport   | biathlon    | basketball | volleyball | snowboarding   |

