.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, photography, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, badminton, baseball, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | photography    | skydiving |
| Sport   | handball   | baseball  | skateboarding | badminton     |

