.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking, baking, reading
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, spanish, thai
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is baking is in an even position##4
3. the chinese is the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the spanish is on the left or right of the chinese##3
5. the chinese is between the thai and the spanish##2
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Hobby         | reading   | baking | camping | filmmaking    |
| Nationality   | spanish | chinese  | thai     | argentine |

