.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, coffee, soy-milk, juice
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, avocado, peach, plum
1. the person eating avocado is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
3. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating peach is on the left of the person eating plum##1
5. the person eating plum is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person eating peach is in an even position##4
7. the person eating pineapple is the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | juice | sprite    | soy-milk       | coffee |
| Food       | avocado  | peach | plum | pineapple  |

