.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, thai, argentine, egyptian
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, car, skateboard, taxi
1. the malaysian is on the left of the egyptian##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the train##3
3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the car is on the right of the argentine##1
5. the malaysian is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the train is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | thai | argentine | malaysian  | egyptian |
| Transport     | train      | skateboard       | car | taxi     |

