.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, nurse, firefighter, social-worker
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, scooter, trike
1. the nurse is in an even position##4
2. the nurse is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
3. the person driving the ship is between the project-manager and the person driving the quad-bike##2
4. the nurse is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the social-worker##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | project-manager | firefighter   | social-worker | nurse |
| Transport   | trike          | ship | quad-bike         | scooter  |

 